instruction:
I want to open the developler tools in chrome with ctrl + shift + i on this website: https://mnsw.pro/
It doesnt work. works on other websites. even here. what is wrong?
output:
It seems that the website you're trying to access has disabled the ability to open the developer tools using the shortcut Ctrl + Shift + I. This is a security measure to prevent unauthorized access to the website's source code and other developer tools.

To access the developer tools on this website, you can try the following:

1. Right-click on the page and select "Inspect" from the context menu. This will open the developer tools.
2. Alternatively, you can try pressing F12 on your keyboard to open the developer tools.

If neither of these methods work, it's possible that the website has further restrictions in place to prevent access to the developer tools. In this case, you may need to contact the website's owner or developer to request access.
